OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting bright and dry
OL,6,FWednesday morning, before increasing
OL,7,Fand thickening cloud brings outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain later in the afternoon with a
OL,9,Ffreshening wind. Much of the rain is
OL,10,Flikely across the Cheviots and
OL,11,FPennines. Some eastern parts perhaps
OL,12,Fremaining dry.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain affecting much
OL,16,Fof the region. Some heavy bursts are
OL,17,Flikely across higher ground. Rain
OL,18,Fclearing during early hours. Gusty
OL,19,Fwinds throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
